  "body": "**Problem**: Nethermind JSON RPC API methods responses donâ€™t return line break at the end of the response and response is stuck together with the next line.\r\n\r\nFor example, now, the response looks like:\r\n```\r\nMacBook-Pro-Viktor:blockscout viktor$ curl -H \"Content-type: application/json\" -X POST --data '{\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\",\"method\":\"eth_blockNumber\",\"id\":1}' http://nethermind\r\n{\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\",\"id\":1,\"result\":\"0x460254\"}MacBook-Pro-Viktor:blockscout viktor$\r\n```\r\n\r\n**Solution**: Add a newline character at the end of all responses\r\n\r\nThus, the above example will look like this:\r\n```\r\nMacBook-Pro-Viktor:blockscout viktor$ curl -H \"Content-type: application/json\" -X POST --data '{\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\",\"method\":\"eth_blockNumber\",\"id\":1}' http://nethermind\r\n{\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\",\"id\":1,\"result\":\"0x460254\"}\r\nMacBook-Pro-Viktor:blockscout viktor$\r\n```\r\n\r\n\r\nThough the linebreak a the end of the response is not a part of a [jsonrpc standard](https://www.jsonrpc.org/specification), it will increase the readability of the response data.",
